  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Thus, studies proposed the concept of \"aggregation of short text\" into regular sized pseudo documents before applying TM.",
    "For example, Pseudo-document-based topic model (Zuo et al. 2016), and Twitter-BTM (Chen et al. 2015b).",
    "Furthermore, based on recent development, the use of neural topic model (NTM) has shown state-of-the-art performances.",
    "This is because these studies benefitted from the embedding models to improve TM results in terms of producing better interpretable topics.",
    "For example, embedded topic model (Dieng et al. 2020), Top2Vec (Angelov 2020), LDA2vec (Moody 2016), and BERTopic (Grootendorst 2022)."
  ],
